Recipe: Salt & Straw Lemon

Ingredients:
  130g sucrose
  18g skim_milk_powder
  1g xanthan
  45g corn_syrup_42
  280g whole_milk
  280g heavy_cream
  120g lemon_juice
  10g lemon_peel
  1g salt

Process Notes:
  Based on Salt & Straw base with lemon juice and zest added.
  Reduced milk/cream slightly to compensate for lemon juice water content.
  Corn syrup helps keep it scoopable despite the acid.
